node.text:
It was an honor to sit down with both the Florida Lt. Governor Jeanette Nuñez and the man who helped capture Che Guevara, Felix Rodriguez. We discussed his life, his time fighting communism, and how many people take freedoms for granted.

In my new book, The Authoritarian Moment, I discuss how the Left is aggressively insistent that everyone must conform to its values, demanding submission, and conformity. Preorder your copy at my link in bio.
